NsbssS'description_long'
p21
S"You are facing are large tree which appears to have a hollow trunk. There is a gap between the tree's root that you believe you can just barely fit through. The gap appears to lead down into the base of the tree."
sS'direction_description'
p22
S'You can head Down in between the roots of the tree, or South to the base of one of the largest trees in the forest.'
