Nsbssg21
S'The circular doorway opens up into a large spherical chamber. From the lowest dip of the curved floor a cylindrical pedestool rises up, terminating at the exact center of the room, where four metal spokes rise from the top and curve inward in proportion to the rest of the rooms dimensions.'
sg22
S'The only exit to this room leads to the South.'
