Nsbssg21
S'The interior of this temple is a smooth, square tunnel leading deep into the heart of the mountain. Shafts of light slice down from long shafts cut through the ceiling of the tunnel, illuminating ancient dust particles that rise into the air with your every footstep. The floor, ceiling, and walls of the tunnel are a dull white, dulled and greyed by the the ravages of time and thick films of dust. To the north of you a circular doorway leads into the heart of the temple.'
sg22
S'You can travel deeper into the temple by heading North through the circular doorway, or walk up the stairs and out into the light by moving South.'
sbsI130
