Nsbssg21
S"You are now standing on a small ledge that juts out from the cliff on the northern side of the river. Glancing up, you can see a tree stump just barely overhanging the edge of the cliff, far above your head. You'd be willing to bet that there would be an excellent view from up there, but you couldn't possibly climb up there with just your bare hands."
sg22
S"You can't climb Up the cliff with your bare hands, so you will have to climb back Down from the ledge, into the river."
