Nsbssg21
S'You are standing inside a small alcove, along the southern shore of the island. This small space between the rocks blocks you from the ocean winds, and keeps out the spray of crashing waves. You sit here and take a few minutes to gather up your thoughts.'
sg22
S'You may only return to the East.'
sbsI125
(iCogObjects
RoomObject
(dp51
g3
I125
sg4
S'You are at the end of the game.'
sg5
S'The last of the original rooms. All of the following rooms have been added to The Cycon Odyssey in order to better balance the game.'
sg6
Nsg7
S'Cycon-Room(125).jpg'
sg8
S'CAVE'
p52
sg9
I0
sg10
(dsg21
S"You now stand before a huge cave entrance that leads underground. You hear some sort of mechanism churning deep below the earth. You sigh, take a deep breathe, and step forward. You've come a long way, and there's no turning back now."
sg22
S'This concludes the first chapter of The Cycon Oddyssey. You have sucessfully overcome many obstacles and mental challanges. I regret that you had to come so far, and you still don\'t know where you are, how you go here, or why you were brought here You don\'t even know what the name "Cycon" means. If you enjoyed this game (or even if you didn\'t) look for The Cycon Odyssey II, \'Tracing Roots\', possibly coming soon to a server near you.'
sbsI124
(iCogObjects
RoomObject
(dp53
g3
I124
sg4
S'You are on a ledge inside of a volcano.'
sg5
S'You need to tie the metal cable onto the metal ring to reach the ledge below you. This room was completely modified later to better round out the game.'
sg6
S'48'
