S'You are able to climb about halfway down the series of ledges before the intervals between ledges becomes too great for you to work your way down any further. There are are many large birds flying around lazily, some of which have roosted in spaces where small crags jut out from the cliff.'
sg22
S'You may only climb back Up to the top of the cliff.'
