S'You have decended down the metal cable, down even closer to the already unbearable heat of the volcano. You are now standing on yet another ledge inside the volcano, on the verge of collapse from heat stroke. Your head is reeling with the warmth of the molten lava splashing below you.'
sg22
S'You may only climp back Up the way you came.'
