sg5
S'Original Text: You have uncovered a tunnel that leads downward, to a large cavern. You slowly crawl through it, and upon reaching the end, your eyes widen and you feel you jaw almost hit the floor. Much to your amazement, there is a huge flat wooden platform ahead of you. On top of the platform is a wide assortment of gears and switches and levers. Behind and above the panels is a huge plate of glass. Astonished and amazed at finding something resembling a computer on an island that seemed so primal you step forward and pull the red handle in front of you...'
