S'The underground tunnel leading downwards widens out here into a small subterrainian chamber. The small species of fungus that grows in the soil of these tunnels seems to grow in a slightly larger form all around the walls of this chamber, creating a much higher level of light than is present in the narrow passageways. In the center of this room sits a small stone pedestool, which is covered with various forms of bizarre pictures and markings, whose possible meaning utterly eludes you.'
sg22
S'The only direction that you can go is back South through the tunnel that led you here.'
