sg5
S'First Transition Text:\012\012You slowly work you way up the side of the hill, along the rock slide. As you near the top of the rock slide you see a rope that is dangling down from the clifftop above you. You grab for the rope as you begin to lose your footing, only to hear a loud snapping sound above, followed by the rope and the dead branch it was tied to falling to the ground just in front of you. You end up sliding back down the hill for a short distance, but finally regain control of your equilibrium and reach the top of the rockslide, where the rope and dried-out tree branch are now laying.'
